import pyximport pyximport.install() from prefixtrie._impl import cPrefixTrie
# Test fuzzy matching behavior trie = cPrefixTrie(['hello'], allow_indels=True)
print("Testing 'heello' with correction_budget=1:") result = trie.search('heello', correction_budget=1) print(f"Result: {result}")
print("\nTesting 'hllo' with correction_budget=1:") result = trie.search('hllo', correction_budget=1) print(f"Result: {result}")
print("\nTesting 'hallo' with correction_budget=1:") result = trie.search('hallo', correction_budget=1) print(f"Result: {result}")
print("\nTesting exact match 'hello':") result = trie.search('hello') print(f"Result: {result}")
print("\nTesting 'heello' without correction budget:") result = trie.search('heello', correction_budget=0) print(f"Result: {result}")
